      $ ARCH_FLAGS="-mtune=nocona" make

    You can find details in the gcc manual:
      http://gcc.gnu.org/onlinedocs/

    You probably want to look in the section:
      "GCC Command Options"
         -> "Hardware Models and Configurations"
             -> "Intel 386 and AMD x86-64 Options"

